find_grey_positions.prompt: find all the grey positions in the input

change_positions_to_blue.prompt: Change the positions of the input coordinates up, down, left, and right to blue

change_corners_to_grey.prompt: Change the positions of the input coordinates from top left, top right, bottom left, and bottom right to grey

change_positions_to_black.prompt: Change the input coordinates to black

main.code:
def main(input):
    positions = "find all the grey positions in the input"(input)
    output = "Change the positions of the input coordinates up, down, left, and right to blue"(input, positions)
    output = "Change the positions of the input coordinates from top left, top right, bottom left, and bottom right to grey"(output, positions)
    output = "Change the input coordinates to black"(output, positions)
    return output
